{"tid":1735210,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"認真講句，請聽咩咩妹一席話","createTime":"2019-11-18T13:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T12:26:47.000Z","uid":102240,"like":18,"dislike":185,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"dadb690bea64939a53b10e9346a8715613c22b4b","tid":1735210,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:33:44.000Z","msg":"願你相信我係真心講，你可以話我失敗主義，但我是出於善意講。<br />\n<br />\n你地到底知唔知出面好危險，不要去，咩咩妹想你們留在家中。<br />\n<br />\n地厚天高拍出唻只係比最出名的人留名，你去送頭最多只係上唻高登開到取暖post。<br />\n<br />\n平時我玩膠就講到自己天下無敵，但有時生命中要接受現實，不要被浪漫主義蓋過理性。<br />\n<br />\n安坐家中祈個禱，總好過白白為你素未謀面的人而坐監，歷史記事不記人。"},{"pid":"4911aa5eb316a5aa463de2d854dac822da13e347","tid":1735210,"uid":4957,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:34:42.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦 屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"825f94b726d7ada31144dd13f97bae4de0efcad4","tid":1735210,"uid":85578,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"882891fe0356de492518d0716b9d59bc3bfbc1b8","tid":1735210,"uid":340080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qV6Vs72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqV6Vs72.jpg&h=70684d44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9717076c9afd19352a992d47a0f7a5fc5a46f23a","tid":1735210,"uid":181217,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"所以做緊冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6df44f28084809fa9339c2724e0c49bc5ae79c","tid":1735210,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WdTgW1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWdTgW1F.jpg&h=12d0054f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e9a0ada0b510f79db6b2bd996d7c56e905e2642","tid":1735210,"uid":26766,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"你